or  in  which  a  labor  dispute  would  hinder  or 
obstruct  commerce  or  the  free  flow  of  commerce, 
and 
industry 
affecting  commerce,  as  defined  in  paragraphs  (1) 
and  (3)  of  section  501  of  the  Labor  Management 
