(II) EMPLOYEE.The term employee has the 
same  meaning  given  such  term  in  section  3(e)  of 
the  Fair  Labor  Standards  Act  of  1938  (29  U.S.C. 
203(e)). 

commerce  and  any 

(III)  PERSON.The  term  person  has  the 
