of the Fair Labor Standards Act of 1938 (29 U.S.C. 
203(a)). 

(3)  FLSA  TERMS.The  terms  employ  and  State  have 
the  meanings  given  such  terms  in  section  3  of  the  Fair  Labor 
Standards Act of 1938 (29 U.S.C. 203). 

