SEC. 6006. APPLICATION WITH RESPECT TO TRICARE, COVERAGE FOR 

VETERANS, AND COVERAGE FOR FEDERAL CIVILIANS. 

(a)  TRICARE.The  Secretary  of  Defense  may  not  require  any 
